{"tid":2314780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡官員稱聖誕至新年期間審視星港旅遊氣泡計劃","createTime":"2020-12-06T18:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T19:55:22.000Z","uid":166360,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"35c3a8668d907d03189b0ebe2ad8920258960ca0","tid":2314780,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"新加坡官員稱聖誕至新年期間審視星港旅遊氣泡計劃<br />\n2020-12-06 HKT 23:16<br />\n<br />\n&quot;新加坡交通部長王乙康表示，將會在聖誕至新年期間，審視啟動新加坡與香港的旅行氣泡計劃......新加坡目前容許來自中國內地、澳洲、文萊、新西蘭和越南的短期旅客入境，毋須隔離檢疫，但抵埗後要接受病毒檢測。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563884-20201206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563884-20201206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2rtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=671320f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563884-20201206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=73ee8c3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563884-20201206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a1e226206a1a0565187217da484a1099cbdd59d3","tid":2314780,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"為奶共 又冇台灣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d375a963452e9b9c77cd73f32398c9fc943d1479","tid":2314780,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:30:35.000Z","msg":"去睇馬嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4131ccd7946b5fbd1397c08ff4adca953c16c62f","tid":2314780,"uid":302471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140d6683e12d68e1310be46ce8ac765190bfc165","tid":2314780,"uid":83874,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18